{"title":"诗人与夜莺","authors":["梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":6,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗人与夜莺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梁上泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位将军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保护着一位诗人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位诗人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保护着一群夜莺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜莺飞来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落翅在一座新城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柔声啼鸣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸣叫在十里丛林。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位青年扛着猎枪逡巡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"装的子弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在把那鸣禽搜寻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不知夜莺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从来是爱情的象征，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对它瞄准，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无异于戕杀爱情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪响鸟落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赢得了片刻欢欣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何曾想到会射穿诗人的心？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此以后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他守望着每个晨昏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象那将军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卫护着这位诗人。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}